<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1598373-i-am-about-done-with-dragons-of-autumn-s">I am about done with Dragons of Autumn&#39;s Twilight. I&#39;ve found that the book seems to have choppy writing and tries very much to cater to the game aspect of the story. While I don&#39;t mind the D&amp;D setting being made into a story, it seems to suffer from trying to hard to make it into a novel. Does the writing smooth out any in book 2?</a>
</div>
